task.summary: edited views for non constant values in butterknife injection
Updated SlidePager to implement its own listener and override the set listener function to allow the user to hook in their own listener
slidepager now has color attr and sildepageradapter has been moved to lib. adapter takes dates and generates views instead of demo app
added tests framework, and tests for getWeeksBetween utilities function
onPageScrolled is but an interface and a super method, so never implement OnPageChangeListener in an adapter
added string-array for the names of the days in a week
animation of day progress works with listeners
added WeekSlideView and linked listeners to each day, replaced inflator in slidepageradapter
